<lb n="0564c25" ed="T"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="001"/><cb:jhead><title>佛說護淨經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="T" n="0564c26"/>
<lb n="0564c27" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">失譯<note n="0564013" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔人〕－【宋】【元】【宮】，人＋（名）【明】</note><note n="0564013" type="mod" resp="CBETA">人【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】，人名【明】</note><app n="0564013"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">人名</rdg></app>今附東晉錄</byline>
<lb ed="T" n="0564c28"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT17p0564c2801"><note n="0564014" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">往昔佛＝佛往昔【三】【宮】</note><note n="0564014" type="mod" resp="CBETA">往昔佛【大】，佛往昔【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0564014"><lem wit="【大】">往昔，佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛往昔</rdg></app>共阿難行，遇值一池，東西四十里，
<lb n="0564c29" ed="T"/>南北四十里，深四十里。池中有虫，其<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0564015" place="foot text">〔形〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0564015">形【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0564015"><lem wit="【大】">形</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>似
<pb xml:id="T17.0748.0565a" n="0565a" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0565a01"/><note place="foot text" n="0565001" resp="Taisho" type="orig">科＝蝌【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565001">科【大】，蝌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565001"><lem wit="【大】">科</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">蝌</rdg></app>蚪，形黑如墨。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0565a0107">佛語阿難：「識此<note place="foot text" n="0565002" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔池中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565002" type="mod" resp="CBETA">池中【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565002"><lem wit="【大】">池中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>虫不？」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0565a02"/><p xml:id="pT17p0565a0201">答言：「不識。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0565a0205" rend="inline">佛語阿難：「此池中虫者，十方世界
<lb n="0565a03" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" n="0565003" resp="Taisho" type="orig">大＝本【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，本【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565003"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">本</rdg></app>眾僧，食不淨食，墮此臭穢糞屎池中，常
<lb ed="T" n="0565a04"/>食不淨，五百萬世中受此苦惱竟；<note n="0565004" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">後＋（復）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後【大】，後復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565004"><lem wit="【大】">後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">後復</rdg></app>五百世
<lb ed="T" n="0565a05"/>中<note place="foot text" n="0565005" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔復〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565005">復【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565005"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>墮餓狗中，常食不淨；<note n="0565006" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">復＝後【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0565006">復【大】，後【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565006"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">後</rdg></app>墮猪中，五百
<lb n="0565a06" ed="T"/><note n="0565007" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">世＋（中復）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】，世中復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565007"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">世中復</rdg></app>常食不淨；復墮蜣<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0565008" place="foot text">蜋＋（蟲）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0565008">蜋【大】，蜋蟲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565008"><lem wit="【大】">蜋</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">蜋蟲</rdg></app>中常食不淨。亦五
<lb ed="T" n="0565a07"/>百世<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0565009" place="foot text">得＝復【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得【大】，復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565009"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復</rdg></app>出為人，常生貧窮<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0565010" place="foot text">家＋（中）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565010">家【大】，家中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565010"><lem wit="【大】">家</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">家中</rdg></app>，衣不覆形，食
<lb n="0565a08" ed="T"/>不充口，常<note place="foot text" n="0565011" resp="Taisho" type="orig">食＋（<g ref="#CB13542"/>䅵）【宋】【宮】，（<g ref="#CB13540"/>䅵）【元】，（籺糕）【明】</note><note n="0565011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，食<g ref="#CB13542"/>䅵【宋】【宮】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->食<g ref="#CB13540"/>䅵【元】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->食籺糕【明】</note><app n="0565011"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">食<g ref="#CB13542"/>䅵</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">食<g ref="#CB13540"/>䅵</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">食籺糕</rdg></app>糠<note place="foot text" n="0565012" resp="Taisho" type="orig">飯＝餅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯【大】，餅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565012"><lem wit="【大】">飯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">餅</rdg></app>，恒飢不足。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0565a0812" rend="inline">佛語諸比丘：
<lb ed="T" n="0565a09"/>「有如是<note n="0565013" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔者〕－【宮】</note><note n="0565013" type="mod" resp="CBETA">者【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0565013"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，受罪尤苦，無量無邊。<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565014">誡＝戒【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0565014">誡【大】，戒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565014"><lem wit="【大】">誡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">戒</rdg></app>語後世
<lb ed="T" n="0565a10"/>末法中，諸比丘不可不慎，一切眾僧有住止
<lb ed="T" n="0565a11"/>處，作不淨食不足<note n="0565015" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">往＝住【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565015" type="mod" resp="CBETA">往【大】，住【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565015"><lem wit="【大】">往</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>食。欲<note n="0565016" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">淨＝得【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565016">淨【大】，得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565016"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得</rdg></app>食者，一切白。
<lb ed="T" n="0565a12"/>衣食如法，著衣持鉢，<note place="foot text" n="0565017" resp="Taisho" type="orig">稱＝攝【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">稱【大】，攝【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565017"><lem wit="【大】">稱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">攝</rdg></app>四威儀，如法往造
<lb n="0565a13" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565018">〔乞〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乞【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565018"><lem wit="【大】">乞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，是真比丘，除其邪命，<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565019">如法活命＝活命如法【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0565019">如法活命【大】，活命如法【宮】</note><app n="0565019"><lem wit="【大】">如法活命</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">活命如法</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0565a1314" rend="inline">「佛不妄
<lb n="0565a14" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565020">言＝語【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，語【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565020"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">語</rdg></app>，福報如影響。往昔比丘，<note n="0565021" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">新＝報【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565021">新【大】，報【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565021"><lem wit="【大】">新</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">報</rdg></app>得阿羅<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565022">漢＋（果）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565022">漢【大】，漢果【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565022"><lem wit="【大】">漢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">漢果</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0565a15" ed="T"/>有結業身，有便利患。<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0565023" place="foot text">夜＝向【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0565023">夜【大】，向【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565023"><lem wit="【大】">夜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">向</rdg></app>闇上廁，見一比丘
<lb ed="T" n="0565a16"/>在廁邊呻吟，阿羅漢語是比丘：『汝本好用<note place="foot text" n="0565024" resp="Taisho" type="orig">意＝行【宮】</note><note n="0565024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意【大】，行【宮】</note><app n="0565024"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">行</rdg></app>
<lb n="0565a17" ed="T"/>人，云何墮餓鬼中呻吟如是？』餓鬼比丘答言：
<lb ed="T" n="0565a18"/>『我<note place="foot text" n="0565025" resp="Taisho" type="orig">餓＝饑【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餓【大】，饑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565025"><lem wit="【大】">餓</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">饑</rdg></app>渴來久，五百餘年不見漿<note n="0565026" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔水〕－【宮】</note><note n="0565026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">水【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0565026"><lem wit="【大】">水</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，正欲趣
<lb ed="T" n="0565a19"/>廁<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0565027" place="foot text">用＝欲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565027" type="mod" resp="CBETA">用【大】，欲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565027"><lem wit="【大】">用</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">欲</rdg></app>食不淨，護廁鬼<note place="foot text" n="0565028" resp="Taisho" type="orig">神＋（手捉）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565028" type="mod" resp="CBETA">神【大】，神手捉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565028"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">神手捉</rdg></app>鐵杖打我，不得近
<lb ed="T" n="0565a20"/>廁。憶念本曾作比丘知<note n="0565029" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">僧＝淨【宋】【元】【宮】，僧＋（淨）【明】</note><note n="0565029" type="mod" resp="CBETA">僧【大】，淨【宋】【元】【宮】，僧淨【明】</note><app n="0565029"><lem wit="【大】">僧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">淨</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">僧淨</rdg></app>事<note place="foot text" n="0565030" resp="Taisho" type="orig">時＝<unclear/>【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565030" type="mod" resp="CBETA">時【大】，<unclear/>【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565030"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><unclear/></rdg></app>，是<note n="0565031" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">用＋（是）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565031" type="mod" resp="CBETA">用【大】，用是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565031"><lem wit="【大】">用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">用是</rdg></app>觸
<lb n="0565a21" ed="T"/>眾僧淨<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565032">〔食〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565032">食【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565032"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，以不淨食<note place="foot text" n="0565033" resp="Taisho" type="orig">食＝飴【三】</note><note n="0565033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，飴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0565033"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">飴</rdg></app>眾僧，故致此殃。』遇
<lb n="0565a22" ed="T"/>值阿羅漢善知識，阿羅漢為比丘<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565034">僧＝眾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565034" type="mod" resp="CBETA">僧【大】，眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565034"><lem wit="【大】">僧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">眾</rdg></app>中燒
<lb n="0565a23" ed="T"/>香呪願，即免餓鬼，還復人道。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0565a2312"><note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0565035" place="foot text">佛＝誡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，誡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565035"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">誡</rdg></app>語諸比丘：
<lb ed="T" n="0565a24"/>「不可不慎，一切不得觸眾僧淨食。佛不虛言，
<lb ed="T" n="0565a25"/>福報如影響，十八地獄經中出罪福。此餓鬼
<lb n="0565a26" ed="T"/><note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0565036" place="foot text">〔本〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565036">本【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565036"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>從人道中來，以不清淨手觸眾僧淨器；
<lb ed="T" n="0565a27"/>以不<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565037">淨手＝清淨手自【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0565037">淨手【大】，清淨手自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565037"><lem wit="【大】">淨手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">清淨手自</rdg></app>觸沙門淨食，以不<note n="0565038" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">（清）＋淨【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0565038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨【大】＊，清淨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0565038"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">清淨</rdg></app>食著沙門
<lb ed="T" n="0565a28"/>淨食中。以不淨食<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565039">食＝飼【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0565039" type="mod" resp="CBETA">食【大】＊，飼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0565039"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飼</rdg></app>眾僧故，後五百世中，
<lb n="0565a29" ed="T"/>墮餓鬼中，常食不淨；欲趣廁上<note n="0565040" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">食糞＝噉糞屎【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食糞【大】，噉糞屎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565040"><lem wit="【大】">食糞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">噉糞屎</rdg></app>，于時廁
<pb xml:id="T17.0748.0565b" n="0565b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0565b01" ed="T"/>神手捉鐵杖打<note place="foot text" n="0565041" resp="Taisho" type="orig">（（之令…膿血））十一字＝（（餓鬼不得近廁此餓鬼常食膿血食人））十五字【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0565041">（之令…膿血）十一字【大】，餓鬼不得近廁此餓鬼常食膿血食人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565041" cb:word-count="11"><lem wit="【大】">之，令不得近。此鬼食人膿
<lb ed="T" n="0565b02"/>血</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">餓鬼不得近廁此餓鬼常食膿血食人</rdg></app>、涕唾及蕩<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565042">滌＝除【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565042" type="mod" resp="CBETA">滌【大】，除【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565042"><lem wit="【大】">滌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">除</rdg></app>惡汁，常<note n="0565043" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">伺＝守【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">伺【大】，守【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565043"><lem wit="【大】">伺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">守</rdg></app>捕婦女<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565044">產＋（藏）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0565044">產【大】，產藏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565044"><lem wit="【大】">產</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">產藏</rdg></app>血不
<lb ed="T" n="0565b03"/>淨，以為飲食。復經<note place="foot text" n="0565045" resp="Taisho" type="orig">五百＋（萬）【宮】</note><note n="0565045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五百【大】，五百萬【宮】</note><app n="0565045"><lem wit="【大】">五百</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">五百萬</rdg></app>世，墮猪、狗、蜣蜋<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565046">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565046" type="mod" resp="CBETA">之【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565046"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0565b04" ed="T"/>中，常食臭<note n="0565047" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">糞＋（穢）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">糞【大】，糞穢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565047"><lem wit="【大】">糞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">糞穢</rdg></app>不淨。受斯苦<note n="0565048" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">劇＋（之中）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">劇【大】，劇之中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565048"><lem wit="【大】">劇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">劇之中</rdg></app>，累世<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565049">如此於百千＝勤苦數千萬【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565049">如此於百千【大】，勤苦數千萬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565049"><lem wit="【大】">如此，
<lb n="0565b05" ed="T"/>於百千</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">勤苦數千萬</rdg></app>劫，無有出期，難得解脫，痛不可言。</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0565b06"/><p xml:id="pT17p0565b0601">「以不淨手觸男根，<note place="foot text" n="0565050" resp="Taisho" type="orig">或＋（手）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565050" type="mod" resp="CBETA">或【大】，或手【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565050"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">或手</rdg></app>觸女根，觸沙門淨器，
<lb ed="T" n="0565b07"/><note n="0565051" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">（以手）＋觸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">觸【大】，以手觸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565051"><lem wit="【大】">觸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">以手觸</rdg></app>沙門淨食；以不淨食，著沙門淨食中；以
<lb n="0565b08" ed="T"/>不淨食<app corresp="#0565039" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飼</rdg></app>眾僧故，致此殃，一切人肉眼不
<lb n="0565b09" ed="T"/>知罪福。自今<note n="0565052" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">以＝已【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0565052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】＊，已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0565052"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>後，欲得福祐，佐眾僧作食，
<lb n="0565b10" ed="T"/>以清淨手捉眾僧淨器、<app type="star" corresp="#0565038"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">清淨</rdg></app>手<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0565053">淘＝濤【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0565053">淘【大】，濤【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0565053"><lem wit="【大】">淘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">濤</rdg></app>米、<note place="foot text" n="0565054" resp="Taisho" type="orig">及＝乃【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565054">及【大】，乃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565054"><lem wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">乃</rdg></app>以
<lb n="0565b11" ed="T"/>淨米著眾僧淨食中<note n="0565055" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565055">者【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565055"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，得福無量。自今<app type="star" corresp="#0565052"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>
<lb n="0565b12" ed="T"/>後，以此為常，一切眾人普使聞<note place="foot text" n="0565056" resp="Taisho" type="orig">知＋（至心奉行）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0565056" type="mod" resp="CBETA">知【大】，知至心奉行【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0565056"><lem wit="【大】">知</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">知至心奉行</rdg></app>。<note n="0565057" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔一切…響〕二百四十六字－【宮】</note><note n="0565057a" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（一切…苦）九十二字【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="92" n="0565057a"><lem wit="【大】">一切檀
<lb n="0565b13" ed="T"/>越施設法會，供齋調度，持齋者得食，不持齋
<lb ed="T" n="0565b14"/>者不得食。此飯一日持齋，得六十萬世餘糧；
<lb ed="T" n="0565b15"/>不持齋者，六十萬世墮餓鬼中。何以故？此信
<lb n="0565b16" ed="T"/>施難銷故。寧吞熱鐵丸，不食此飯。吞熱鐵丸，
<lb n="0565b17" ed="T"/>須臾間耳，食<note n="0565058" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔此〕－【三】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565058">此【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0565058"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>信施，久受大苦，五百萬世
<lb n="0565b18" ed="T"/>中受餓鬼苦。</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0565057b">（諸有…響）一百五十四字【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0565057b"><lem wit="【大】"><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0565b1806">「諸有設食之處，一切如法作齋，
<lb ed="T" n="0565b19"/>不得懷挾餘殘食，歸給妻子。若食此飯，若腋
<lb ed="T" n="0565b20"/>底挾擔，後五百<note place="foot text" n="0565059" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔世〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0565059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0565059"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，常挾熱鐵輪，左腋底入
<lb n="0565b21" ed="T"/>從右腋底出。一切齋飯不可不慎，一米化作
<lb ed="T" n="0565b22"/>熱丸。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0565b2203" rend="inline">「一切賢者施設福會，於先嘗啜此食，都
<lb n="0565b23" ed="T"/>作殘食，唐作此會，不如不作。何以故？諸天不
<lb n="0565b24" ed="T"/>歡，鬼神不喜。此人於先甞者，亦五百世中受
<lb ed="T" n="0565b25"/>餓鬼苦。自今已後，欲得福者，如法作齋食，可
<lb ed="T" n="0565b26"/>得福德，諸天歡喜，百神慶悅，天神擁護。經不
<lb n="0565b27" ed="T"/>虛言，福報如影響。」</p></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:div>
